First Department,

August, 1952.

(August 14,1952.) In the Matter of William J. Bianchi, Appellant, against William J. Heffernan et al., Constituting the Board of Elections of the City of New York, et al., Respondents.

Order unanimously affirmed. No opinion. Present — Peek, P. J., Dore, Cohn, Callahan and Van Voorhis, JJ.
